# =========================================================================
# DATABASE CONFIGURATION (SUPABASE POSTGRESQL)
# =========================================================================

# 1. DATABASE_URL: Used by Prisma Client for queries.
# Jika koneksi direct (port 5432) tidak bisa terhubung karena jaringan IPv4,
# gunakan connection string "Session Pooler" (port 6543) dari Supabase Anda.
# Contoh format: postgresql://postgres.[PROJECT_REF]:[YOUR-PASSWORD]@[PROJECT_REF].pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres?pgbouncer=true
DATABASE_URL=""

# 2. DIRECT_URL: Digunakan untuk migrasi database oleh Prisma (non-pooled direct connection)
# Ganti [YOUR-PASSWORD] dengan password database yang Anda buat saat setup Supabase.
DIRECT_URL=""